STATE
v.
ANDERSON 2019-0788 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 21, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On review of order certifying a conflict. The court determines that a conflict exists. Sua sponte, cause held for the decision in 2017-1703, State v. Dangler, and briefing schedule stayed. French, J., dissents.
